<p><i>"If you are not willing to die for what is in the Bible, you should not give money for Bibles.&nbsp; Because if you give, we will smuggle more Bibles.&nbsp; And if we smuggle more Bibles, there will be more martyrs."&nbsp;</i>&nbsp;<br><i>-Richard Wurmbrand (Founder of Voice of the Martyrs)</i></p><h3><strong>MISSION FIELD PRAYER COVER</strong></h3><p>Please continue your PRAYER cover for missionaries worldwide, the need is great, and the workers are few. Thank you.</p><ul><li>PRAY for:&nbsp;<ul><li>families of missionaries&nbsp;</li><li>protection and provision</li><li>all materials reach their destination without hinderance</li><li>The LORD's divine health</li></ul></li></ul><h3><strong>MISSIONS IN HAITI</strong></h3><p><i><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/MISSIONS/t_gary-haiti2.jpg" alt="Bibles for Haiti"></i></p><ul><li>Trip Sept. 21, 2023 (2 weeks)</li><li>Pray for the people of Haiti</li><li><i>Photo: Bibles for Haiti in Kreol</i></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/PDF/haiti-needs.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff;"><u>Letter from Gary's desk - ministry needs</u></span></a></li></ul><h3><strong>MISSIONS IN HONG KONG/CHINA</strong></h3><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/MISSIONS/main-gate.jpg" alt="Main gate at a famous University in Southern China" width="200" height="150"></p><ul><li>April 2020</li><li><i>Photo: famous University in main land China</i></li><li>Pray for China to reopen for Westerners</li></ul><h3><strong>MISSIONS IN DOMINICAN REPUBLIC</strong></h3><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/MISSIONS/t_score-dr.jpg" alt="Score International Ministry in Dominican Republic"></p><ul><li>November &nbsp;2019</li><li>This mission trip is with Score International. Need more information about the organization? <a href="https://scoreintl.org/trips/dominican-republic/">SCORE International - Dominican</a></li><li>This is an ongoing mission venture with Score Intl.</li></ul><h3><strong>MISSIONS HONG KONG/CHINA</strong></h3><h3><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/MISSIONS/t_china-girl.jpg" alt="Preschool children in Southern China"></h3><ul><li>July/August 2019</li><li>This mission trip to China is coming up soon!&nbsp; If you are interested in joining us, let us know.</li><li><i>Photo: preschool children in Southern China</i></li></ul><h3><strong>PRAYER POINTS</strong></h3><ul><li>Pray for creative ways of delivering Bibles in hostile nations.</li><li>Pray for missionaries worldwide and their families (financial support, endued with power from the Holy Spirit, divine health and protection).</li><li>Pray for salvation throughout the earth.</li></ul><h3><strong>NEWSLETTERS (PDF)</strong></h3><p><strong><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/Gary-bus1.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300"></strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/PDF/haiti-needs.pdf">Haiti Missions - Ministry Needs 2023</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/fill-the-bus-haiti.pdf">Haiti Missions - Fill the Bus April 2019</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/Haiti-Missions-update-Oct2018.pdf">Haiti Missions Update - Oct. 2018</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/Haiti-missions-report-July2018.pdf">MISSION NEWS from Haiti-July2018</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/donations4Haiti.pdf">Haiti Donations List</a></li></ul><h3><strong>ARTICLES - INFORMATION</strong></h3><ul><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/Abounding_Love-missionsCOLOMBIA-2016.pdf">Abounding LOVE - Colombia Missions Trip</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/eniths_story.pdf">Enith's Story - How much does it cost?</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/Haiti-missions-report-July2018.pdf">Haiti Missions Report</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/China-News2016.pdf">Roz's Mission News - CHINA</a></li><li><a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/MISSIONS/PrayerCard_In